    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/4d268bff548148191c2bcab313c6b0b7.avif?t=1767366451\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《The Saint 圣徒》</strong>是一款第一人称心理恐怖游戏，灵感来源于《寂静岭》等经典恐怖作品。你将在如梦似幻的中间空间中游荡——遗忘的走廊、扭曲的大厅、无尽的迷雾，仿佛置身于老旧VHS录像带的模糊画面中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里的现实是破碎的。<br>时间在循环。<br>沉默中传来低语。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片荒诞世界中探索，解开象征性的谜题，对抗心理崩溃的边缘，而那无法名状的存在，正悄然逼近。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《The Saint》不仅仅是游戏——它是一次坠入未知深渊的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能逃离那原本不该被发现的东西吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/3f80355edc6e8b9e03c04c1938c6cf2e.poster.avif?t=1767366451\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/3f80355edc6e8b9e03c04c1938c6cf2e.webm?t=1767366451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/3f80355edc6e8b9e03c04c1938c6cf2e.mp4?t=1767366451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/e94a1219ec851bea9f1915354e690ffe.avif?t=1767366451\" width=614 height=154 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🕯️ 沉浸式心理恐怖体验</strong><br>受到《寂静岭2》启发，深入雾气弥漫、充满压迫感的世界，每个角落都充满未知恐惧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🧠 精神错乱与恐惧交织</strong><br>没有廉价的惊吓，只有持续不断的不安氛围和令人困惑的现实扭曲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🏚️ 中间空间与压抑沉默</strong><br>穿梭于空荡荡的办公楼层、重复的房间与永无止境的楼梯，仿佛自己被困在时间的缝隙中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🧩 象征性谜题与隐藏线索</strong><br>谜题不仅考验思维，更揭示主角内心的秘密与恐惧。每一扇门背后，可能藏着真相……或更深的绝望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🌫️ 扭曲现实与心理幻觉</strong><br>世界在你面前改变，记忆变得模糊，时间失去意义。你还能相信眼前所见吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/0d132abe808ec208a7bb14afcab69894.poster.avif?t=1767366451\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/0d132abe808ec208a7bb14afcab69894.webm?t=1767366451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/0d132abe808ec208a7bb14afcab69894.mp4?t=1767366451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/21bce87c8752ed805e32e9007775c21a.poster.avif?t=1767366451\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/21bce87c8752ed805e32e9007775c21a.webm?t=1767366451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/21bce87c8752ed805e32e9007775c21a.mp4?t=1767366451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/ac834f0f530137ddef413563c4cdcb31.poster.avif?t=1767366451\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/ac834f0f530137ddef413563c4cdcb31.webm?t=1767366451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/ac834f0f530137ddef413563c4cdcb31.mp4?t=1767366451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1767366451\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1767366451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005210/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1767366451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
